reviewText: Well i can't say it was to bad,because that was back in 05' versus 2012. An a lot of quality of things have changed scene then. Ok I'll say "great".

awsume, i would highly recommend it to any superbike fan. the speed,and changing weather conditions make it tough for the riders who have to make a critical decision on what tires to use,rain or shine you have all the excitment a sports bike fan can want and then some!
